Import Data Channel- Returning Users

DA <-  read_excel("~/Desktop/Job related/Surefoot/Surefoot 2/Surefoot- GA/Analysis - 2/test and control dates/Returned Users+Channel/Returning Users-Channel.xlsx", sheet = 2)

Data wrangling

DA_01 <- DA 
 
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Default Channel Grouping"] <- "Channel" 
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Date Range"] <- "Date_Range" 
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="New Users"] <- "New_Users"
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Bounce Rate"] <- "Bounce_Rate"
  

DA_02 <- DA_01 %>% filter(!is.na(Channel))

DA_03 <- DA_02 %>% mutate(test_categ = ifelse(Date_Range == "Oct 18, 2019 - Oct 31, 2019", "test-Oct 18,2019 - Oct 31,2019", "control-Oct 4,2019 - Oct 17,2019"))

DA_m <- DA_03 %>% filter(Date_Range == "Oct 18, 2019 - Oct 31, 2019")

Visualization Channel-Returning Users count

DA_03 %>% filter(Users > 0 ) %>% ggplot() + geom_histogram(aes(Users), binwidth = 500, fill = "blue",col = "black") + facet_wrap(~test_categ)

DA_03 %>%
  group_by(Channel) %>%
  ggplot(aes(reorder(x =  as.factor(Channel), Users),  y=Users)) + geom_bar(stat = 'identity', fill = "coral1") + ggtitle("Fig. 1 Channels used by Returning Users") + geom_text(aes(label=Users), size = 2.5, position=position_dodge(width=0.2), vjust=-0.25) + theme(plot.title = element_text(size =10),axis.text.x = element_text(size =7,angle = 45, hjust = 1))  + xlab("Channels") +ylab("User Counts")+ facet_wrap(~test_categ)

Channel-Returning Users-Sessions

DA_03 %>%
  group_by(Channel) %>%
  ggplot(aes(reorder(x =  as.factor(Channel), Sessions),  y=Sessions)) + geom_bar(stat = 'identity', fill = "coral1") + ggtitle("Fig. 2 Sessions in Channels used by Returning Users") + geom_text(aes(label=Sessions), size = 2.5, position=position_dodge(width=0.2), vjust=-0.25) + theme(plot.title = element_text(size =10),axis.text.x = element_text(size =7,angle = 45, hjust = 1))  + xlab("Channels") +ylab("Sessions")+ facet_wrap(~test_categ)

Channel-Returning Users-Bounce Rate

DA_03_01 <- DA_03 %>% mutate(Bounce_Rt = round(Bounce_Rate*100,2))
DA_03_01 %>%
  group_by(Channel) %>%
  ggplot(aes(reorder(x =  as.factor(Channel), Bounce_Rt),  y=Bounce_Rt)) + geom_bar(stat = 'identity', fill = "coral1") + ggtitle("Fig. 3 Bounce Rate % in Channels used by Returning Users") + geom_text(aes(label=Bounce_Rt), size = 2.5, position=position_dodge(width=0.2), vjust=-0.25) + theme(plot.title = element_text(size =10),axis.text.x = element_text(size =7,angle = 45, hjust = 1))  + xlab("Channels") +ylab("Bounce Rate")+ facet_wrap(~test_categ)

Channel-Returning Users-Revenue

DA_03 %>%
  group_by(Channel) %>%
  ggplot(aes(reorder(x =  as.factor(Channel), Revenue),  y=Revenue)) + geom_bar(stat = 'identity', fill = "coral1") + ggtitle("Fig. 4 Revenue in Channels from Returning Users") + geom_text(aes(label=Revenue), size = 2.5, position=position_dodge(width=0.2), vjust=-0.25) + theme(plot.title = element_text(size =10),axis.text.x = element_text(size =7,angle = 45, hjust = 1))  + xlab("Channels") +ylab("Revenue")+ facet_wrap(~test_categ)
